textBeforeTable: Castrol Index Week 13 Top 10 Performers   Make sure to vote for the save by 11:59 PT on Thursday, May 30. CLICK HERE TO VOTE FERNANDEZ!   Fernandez had six stops in the victory, including a couple late match stops to preserve the win. It was Fernandez’s fifth shutout of the season, tied for second-most in MLS.  After a strong performance in goal against San Jose, the honors are pouring in for Raul Fernandez!
